apihelp-growthinvalidateimagerecommendat:
Appellar iste API:

* reinitialisara le [[mw:wikitech:Add_Image|etiquetta ponderate "hasrecommendation:image"]] pro le articulo, de maniera que le articulo non apparera plus in le resultatos de recerca pro suggestiones de imagines;

* addera le articulo a un cache de curte durata, consultate per le extension [[mw:Extension:GrowthExperiments|GrowthExperiments]] pro decider si le articulo debe esser excludite del cauda de modificationes suggerite del usator quando ille los accede sur [[Special:Homepage]] o a transverso le API [[Special:ApiHelp/query+growthtasks|action=query&list=growthtasks]];

* generara e inviara un evento a EventGate al [https://schema.wikimedia.org/#!/secondary/jsonschema/mediawiki/page/image-suggestions-feedback fluxo image-suggestion-feedback], permittente meliorar le tubo de suggestiones de imagines, perque le codice in le tubo pote tener conto del commentos de usatores durante le generation de recommendationes.

Ulterior lectura: [[mw:Growth/Personalized_first_day/Structured_tasks/Add_an_image]]
